{
    "version": "pending",
    "description": "Jujutsu/jj 的终端用户界面 (TUI) | TUI for Jujutsu/jj",
    "homepage": "https://github.com/Cretezy/lazyjj",
    "license": {
        "identifier": "Apache-2.0"
    },
    "notes": [
        "It seems that lazyjj does not pay much attention to the Windows platform.",
        "Although it is still being updated, it no longer releases binary files for the Windows platform.",
        "Jujutsu/jj is in version v0 and iterates rapidly at a frequency of one new version per month.",
        "The stagnation of lazyjj's version may affect the user experience of Jujutsu/jj, so it is converted to pending.",
        "It is currently recommended to use 'IbrahimDursun.jjui'"
    ],
    "notes_cn": [
        "lazyjj 似乎并不重视 Windows 平台。",
        "虽然它目前仍在更新，却没有再发布 Windows 平台的二进制文件。",
        "而 Jujutsu/jj 处于 v0 版本，以每个月一个新版本的频率快速迭代。",
        "lazyjj 的版本停滞可能影响到 Jujutsu/jj 的使用体验，因此将其转为 pending。",
        "目前建议使用 IbrahimDursun.jjui"
    ],
    "architecture": {
        "64bit": {
            "url": "https://github.com/abgox/abyss/releases/download/empty/empty",
            "hash": "36a9e7f1c95b82ffb99743e0c5c4ce95d83c9a430aac59f84ef3cbfab6145068"
        }
    },
    "extract_to": "app",
    "bin": "app\\lazyjj.exe",
    "pre_install": [
        "if (!$bucket) { $bucket = (scoop config).'abgox-abyss-bucket-name' }",
        ". $bucketsdir\\$bucket\\script\\utils.ps1",
        "A-Start-Install"
    ],
    "post_install": [
        "if (!$bucket) { $bucket = (scoop config).'abgox-abyss-bucket-name' }",
        ". $bucketsdir\\$bucket\\script\\utils.ps1",
        "A-Complete-Install"
    ],
    "pre_uninstall": [
        "if (!$bucket) { $bucket = (scoop config).'abgox-abyss-bucket-name' }",
        ". $bucketsdir\\$bucket\\script\\utils.ps1",
        "A-Start-Uninstall",
        "A-Stop-Process"
    ],
    "post_uninstall": [
        "if (!$bucket) { $bucket = (scoop config).'abgox-abyss-bucket-name' }",
        ". $bucketsdir\\$bucket\\script\\utils.ps1",
        "A-Complete-Uninstall"
    ],
    "checkver": {
        "script": [
            ". $pwd\\script\\utils.ps1",
            "A-Get-VersionFromGithubAPI"
        ],
        "regex": "(.+)"
    },
    "autoupdate": {
        "architecture": {
            "64bit": {
                "url": "https://github.com/Cretezy/lazyjj/releases/download/v$version/lazyjj-v$version-x86_64-pc-windows-msvc.zip"
            }
        },
        "hash": {
            "mode": "github"
        }
    }
}
